Package: MedicaidExpansionHEOR
Title: Staggered DiD (Callaway-Sant'Anna) for Medicaid expansion, HEOR-framed
Version: 0.1.0
Description: R dependencies for the headline causal estimators. Pin with
    renv::init(); renv::snapshot() to produce renv.lock (R 4.4.x). The Python pipeline
    (requirements.txt) orchestrates and runs the HEOR/PSA; these R packages run the
    staggered-DiD frontier. If R is unavailable, the tested Python implementation in
    pipeline/csa.py reproduces the same results JSON (plan §11 Q4).
Depends: R (>= 4.4.0)
Imports:
    did,
    fixest,
    bacondecomp,
    fwildclusterboot,
    arrow,
    jsonlite,
    yaml
Encoding: UTF-8
